public class Identity extends com.google.api.client.json.GenericJson
Users are uniquely identified by their email across all of FreshBooks, so if leafy@example.com is an Owner of one account and gets added as a Client on another, they will have some access to both. They could then open a second business of their own, or be added as an employee of another personâ€™s business.
